                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>We are living in extraordinary times. We offer each other unique challenges to our individual modes of thinking. As we immerse ourselves in a breadth of experiences and opportunities at this cosmopolitan institution, let's not forget the sacred value of intellectual diversity.</p>
<p><em>Sabriyya Pate is a Trinity sophomore. Her column, “in formation,” runs on alternate Mondays.</em></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-style: italic; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"></span></p>
